  "detailed_description": "<strong>A Kawaii Kana Match-Em Up.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/725850/extras/40bca565a29dba7c76ce6bf955f2e030.avif?t=1731580694\" width=480 height=81 /></span><br>Are you sick of educational games that are glorified pop-quizzes? Do you just want to play an awesome game and have a new real world skill at the end of it? Do you want to learn how to read Hiragana and Katakana?<br><br>Well then, Kana Quest is for you!<br><br>\"But how does it work\" I hear you think. Excellent question! In Japanese, each phonetic letter is called a Kana. Kana that have a shared sound will match. When all Kana in a level are connected by matches, it will be complete.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful pixel art<br></li><li>Over 300 challenging puzzle levels<br></li><li>Hiragana and Katakana included<br></li><li>Great way to learn for beginners of Japanese<br></li><li>Still a great puzzle game for people who know Japanese<br></li><li>No pop quizzes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/725850/extras/477da3153d1e5d65fa80bbe9f0b65a78.webp?t=1731580694\" width=520 height=52 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>A Kawaii Kana Match-Em Up.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/725850/extras/40bca565a29dba7c76ce6bf955f2e030.avif?t=1731580694\" width=480 height=81 /></span><br>Are you sick of educational games that are glorified pop-quizzes? Do you just want to play an awesome game and have a new real world skill at the end of it? Do you want to learn how to read Hiragana and Katakana?<br><br>Well then, Kana Quest is for you!<br><br>\"But how does it work\" I hear you think. Excellent question! In Japanese, each phonetic letter is called a Kana. Kana that have a shared sound will match. When all Kana in a level are connected by matches, it will be complete.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful pixel art<br></li><li>Over 300 challenging puzzle levels<br></li><li>Hiragana and Katakana included<br></li><li>Great way to learn for beginners of Japanese<br></li><li>Still a great puzzle game for people who know Japanese<br></li><li>No pop quizzes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/725850/extras/477da3153d1e5d65fa80bbe9f0b65a78.webp?t=1731580694\" width=520 height=52 /></span>",
